# ── Vendored pjsua2 payload ────────────────────────────────────────
# Large (~30 MB of .so) and reproducible — COPIED from ../android/pjsua2
# (which is itself regenerated by android/scripts/build-pjsip.sh). Kept out of
# git like the android/ copy; repopulate with:
#   cp -r ../android/pjsua2/src android-watch/pjsua2/src
# The module's build.gradle.kts / README.md above these dirs stay tracked.
pjsua2/src/main/jniLibs/
pjsua2/src/main/java/org/pjsip/pjsua2/

